    "## Take Home Messages 📌\n",
    "\n",
    "- The **CEMS Early Warning Data Store (EWDS)** provides free access to GloFAS data products via both a web interface and a Python API\n",
    "- **GloFAS Reanalysis** is a long historical record of river discharge that forms the basis for flood threshold calculation and forecast verification\n",
    "- **earthkit-data** simplifies data access from the EWDS and returns objects that convert seamlessly to `xarray` and `pandas`\n",
    "- River discharge shows strong **seasonal patterns** that must be understood before defining flood thresholds\n",
    "- The `sel(method='nearest')` technique in xarray lets you extract time series at any point location from gridded data"
